                <div class="kt-menu-item " data-navpath="/tutorial/thermal-physics" data-navhref="/tutorial/thermal-physics">
    <div class="kt-accordion-item">
        <a class="kt-menu-link accordion-sub-item" tabindex="0" title="The distinction between heat and temperature is thoroughly explained. Methods of heat transfer are explained. The mathematics associated with temperature changes and phase changes is discussed; its application to the science of calorimetry is presented." href="/tutorial/thermal-physics" aria-label="The distinction between heat and temperature is thoroughly explained. Methods of heat transfer are explained. The mathematics associated with temperature changes and phase changes is discussed; its application to the science of calorimetry is presented." role="link">
            <span class="kt-menu-title">Thermal Physics</span>
        </a>
    </div>
