    <div class="kt-accordion-item">
        <a class="kt-menu-link accordion-sub-item" tabindex="0" title="Our Work, Energy, and Power unit represents an effort to present a model of energy as a tool for analyzing the motion of an object. The model relies on the confidence that energy can be kept track of; and because it can, we are able to make predictions of how fast an object will move, how hight it will go, and how far it will slide. The set of Video Tutorials below describe all sorts of applications of work and energy to the analysis of physical situations." href="/video-tutorial/work-and-energy" aria-label="Our Work, Energy, and Power unit represents an effort to present a model of energy as a tool for analyzing the motion of an object. The model relies on the confidence that energy can be kept track of; and because it can, we are able to make predictions of how fast an object will move, how hight it will go, and how far it will slide. The set of Video Tutorials below describe all sorts of applications of work and energy to the analysis of physical situations." role="link">
            <span class="kt-menu-title">Work and Energy (12)</span>
        </a>
    </div>
