<li data-navpath="/video-tutorial/1d-kinematics" data-navhref="/video-tutorial/1d-kinematics">
    <a class="visually-hidden-focusable" aria-keyshortcuts="ArrowUp ArrowDown Left Right" title="his collection of Physics videos provides an organized presentation of commonly covered physics concepts and principles taught in an introductory Physics course. " href="/video-tutorial/1d-kinematics" aria-label="his collection of Physics videos provides an organized presentation of commonly covered physics concepts and principles taught in an introductory Physics course." role="link">
        1D Kinematics (16)
