<li data-navpath="/video-tutorial/newtons-laws" data-navhref="/video-tutorial/newtons-laws">
    <a class="visually-hidden-focusable" aria-keyshortcuts="ArrowUp ArrowDown Left Right" title="Newton&#x27;s Laws represent an effort to explain the relationship between the motion of an object and the forces that act upon it.  The set of Video Tutorials below explain how forces can affect the motion of objects." href="/video-tutorial/newtons-laws" aria-label="Newton&#x27;s Laws represent an effort to explain the relationship between the motion of an object and the forces that act upon it.  The set of Video Tutorials below explain how forces can affect the motion of objects." role="link">
        Newton's Laws (20)
