<li data-navpath="/video-tutorial/light-waves-and-colors" data-navhref="/video-tutorial/light-waves-and-colors">
    <a class="visually-hidden-focusable" aria-keyshortcuts="ArrowUp ArrowDown Left Right" title="Our Light Waves and Color unit represents an effort to show the variety of wavelike behaviors of light.  The set of Video Tutorials below describe all sorts of applications of light waves, in particular applications to understanding the world of color and light interference." href="/video-tutorial/light-waves-and-colors" aria-label="Our Light Waves and Color unit represents an effort to show the variety of wavelike behaviors of light.  The set of Video Tutorials below describe all sorts of applications of light waves, in particular applications to understanding the world of color and light interference." role="link">
        Light Waves and Colors (13)
    </a>
